overview: On July 3rd GCW present Rock-N-Roll Forever live on FITE straight from Veterans Memorial Coliseum in Evansville, IN. The event features Rock-N-Roll final match at Evansville Coliseum. In this match Rock-N-Roll Express face off The Rejects.  Also in the lineup:  Joey Janela vs Cole Radrick  Jordan Oliver vs Calvin Tankman  Dark Sheik vs Billie Starkz  Tony Deppen vs Kerry Morton  Nick Gage
title: GCW Rock-N-Roll Forever
